This paper deals with the use of blockchain and statistical methods for anomaly detection in IIoT logs. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Databases (cs.DB).
